(1798, 55, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"1fae578\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"20\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"029d0de\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/e-ticaret\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/11\\/ne-okusam.png\",\"id\":364,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"image_size\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d66fe9e\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"boxed_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":924,\"sizes\":[]},\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"50\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4402df0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3><strong>Ne Okusam? \\u00c7ocuk Kitaplar\\u0131yla Renkli Bir D\\u00fcnyaya Yolculuk<\\/strong><\\/h3><p>\\u00c7ocuk kitaplar\\u0131, sadece e\\u011flenceli bir okuma deneyimi sunmakla kalmaz, ayn\\u0131 zamanda \\u00e7ocuklar\\u0131n hayal g\\u00fc\\u00e7lerini besler, empati yeteneklerini geli\\u015ftirir ve onlara de\\u011ferli ya\\u015fam dersleri verir. \\\"Ne Okusam?\\\" sayfam\\u0131zda, her ya\\u015ftan \\u00e7ocu\\u011fa hitap edebilecek kitap \\u00f6nerilerimizi ke\\u015ffedin!<\\/p><h4><strong>1. K\\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fck Okurlar i\\u00e7in E\\u011flenceli Kitaplar<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Okuma al\\u0131\\u015fkanl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 kazand\\u0131rmak i\\u00e7in renkli ve e\\u011flenceli hik\\u00e2yeler vazge\\u00e7ilmezdir. \\u0130\\u015fte bu kategori i\\u00e7in \\u00f6nerilerimiz:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Eric Carle - A\\u00e7 T\\u0131rt\\u0131l<\\/strong>: \\u00c7ocuklar\\u0131n do\\u011fa ve say\\u0131larla tan\\u0131\\u015fmas\\u0131n\\u0131 e\\u011flenceli bir \\u015fekilde sa\\u011flayan klasik bir hik\\u00e2ye.<\\/li><li><strong>Julia Donaldson - Gruffalo<\\/strong>: Cesaret ve dostluk \\u00fczerine s\\u00fcr\\u00fckleyici bir hik\\u00e2ye.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>2. Okuma Becerisini Geli\\u015ftiren Hik\\u00e2yeler<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>Yeni okumaya ba\\u015flayan \\u00e7ocuklar i\\u00e7in bol resimli ve k\\u0131sa metinli kitaplar:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Dr. Seuss - Ye\\u015fil Yumurta ve Salam<\\/strong>: E\\u011flenceli tekerlemelerle dolu bir klasik.<\\/li><li><strong>Beatrix Potter - Tav\\u015fan Peter\\u2019\\u0131n Hik\\u00e2yesi<\\/strong>: Haylaz bir tav\\u015fan\\u0131n maceralar\\u0131.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>3. Hayal G\\u00fcc\\u00fcn\\u00fc G\\u00fc\\u00e7lendiren Kitaplar<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>\\u00c7ocuklar\\u0131n yarat\\u0131c\\u0131l\\u0131klar\\u0131n\\u0131 art\\u0131racak b\\u00fcy\\u00fcleyici hik\\u00e2yeler:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Roald Dahl - B\\u00fcy\\u00fck Sevimli Dev (BFG)<\\/strong>: Fantastik d\\u00fcnyalarda yolculu\\u011fa \\u00e7\\u0131kmak isteyenler i\\u00e7in harika bir se\\u00e7im.<\\/li><li><strong>Lewis Carroll - Alice Harikalar Diyar\\u0131nda<\\/strong>: Hayal g\\u00fcc\\u00fcn\\u00fcn s\\u0131n\\u0131rlar\\u0131n\\u0131 zorlayan bir klasik.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>4. Ya\\u015fama Dair Dersler Veren Hik\\u00e2yeler<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>\\u00c7ocuklara dostluk, yard\\u0131mla\\u015fma ve do\\u011fa sevgisi gibi de\\u011ferleri \\u00f6\\u011freten kitaplar:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Shel Silverstein - Vermeyen A\\u011fa\\u00e7<\\/strong>: \\u015eefkat ve fedakarl\\u0131k \\u00fczerine dokunakl\\u0131 bir hik\\u00e2ye.<\\/li><li><strong>Feridun Oral - K\\u0131rm\\u0131z\\u0131 Elma<\\/strong>: Yard\\u0131mla\\u015fman\\u0131n g\\u00fczelli\\u011fini anlatan s\\u0131cac\\u0131k bir masal.<\\/li><\\/ul><h4><strong>Son S\\u00f6z<\\/strong><\\/h4><p>\\u00c7ocuklar i\\u00e7in kitap se\\u00e7imi, onlar\\u0131n ilgi alanlar\\u0131n\\u0131 ve ya\\u015flar\\u0131n\\u0131 g\\u00f6z \\u00f6n\\u00fcnde bulundurarak yap\\u0131lmal\\u0131d\\u0131r. Kitaplar sadece bilgi sunmaz, ayn\\u0131 zamanda e\\u011flenceyi, sevgiyi ve hayal d\\u00fcnyas\\u0131n\\u0131n kap\\u0131lar\\u0131n\\u0131 da a\\u00e7ar. \\u00c7ocu\\u011funuzun yeni bir maceraya at\\u0131lmas\\u0131na yard\\u0131mc\\u0131 olun ve birlikte okuman\\u0131n keyfini \\u00e7\\u0131kar\\u0131n!<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"left\",\"text_color\":\"#484848\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
